= On-Board MCP23017 32-bit Port Expanders Examples =

<img src="http://land-boards.com/blwiki/images/d/de/PiPicoMite-02_P18268_720px.jpg"></img>

Exercise the MCP23017 32-bit Port Expanders on the [http://land-boards.com/blwiki/index.php?title=PiPicoMite02 PiPicoMite02] card

* [https://github.com/land-boards/RasPiPico/blob/main/PicoMite_MMBASIC/PicoMite_VGA/Land%20Boards%20BASIC%20Programs/lbcards/GPIO32/GPIO32-01.bas GPIO32-01.bas]
** Test the (2) MCP23017 parts on the PiPicoMite02 card
** Light all of the output pins one at a time
** Alternate patterns then bounce a LED
** Operates a byte at a time
** Attached to [http://land-boards.com/blwiki/index.php?title=LED-32 LED-32] card
* [https://github.com/land-boards/RasPiPico/blob/main/PicoMite_MMBASIC/PicoMite_VGA/Land%20Boards%20BASIC%20Programs/lbcards/GPIO32/GPIO32_Bits.bas GPIO32_Bits.bas]
